description: These emojis are in so much pain and they are so sick that they might not even display correctly in all browsers. If you are having issues seeing these Japanese emotes display properly, try changing to a different browser. I have found that Safari usually works better than Internet Explorer, Chrome, or Firefox. One you get them to work, you will love how complex and unique these emojis are.
